    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a great car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a few miles of memories on it, but it runs like a dream and has been well-loved. Come on by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the one for you!",
