    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. It features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a full VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec bushings, providing precise feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response and that signature metallic induction note. An excellent candidate for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
