    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality, having been cared for with an eye for detail. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the slightest signs of careful use that one would expect from a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery remains supple and free of any significant wear, while every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent comprehensive inspection and full fluid service already completed. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the tires offer plenty of life for the road ahead. We have kept a meticulous log of all maintenance, ensuring the next owner can drive away with complete peace of mind. Whether you are looking for a reliable daily commuter or a weekend cruiser, this car delivers a premium experience and exceptional value.",
      "price": 36450.0,
